Use Ansible playbooks to finish the homework

homework.sh - run this shell script to execute the playbooks.
hosts - Ansible host file
index.php - showing PHP info and used by the playbook phpinfo.yml
nginx.default.conf - Nginx default settings to pass PHP request to PHP-FPM
nginx.repo.j2 - template file used by the playbook nginx.yml
nginx.yml - install Nginx
nginx_php.yml - set up PHP settings on Nginx virtual host config
php.yml - install PHP-FPM
phpinfo.yml - Copy index.php to the default path of Nginx web service
README - this file. 

